---
title: Nan's Chorizo, Chicken & Veggie Risotto with Parmesan
description: We believe weeknight dinners should be tasty and on the table without too much fuss. Hence, we present you with our oven-baked chorizo and chicken risotto. Minimal stirring, loads of comforting ooziness and superbly satisfying — what could be better?
